        "jsCode": "// Get today's boundaries in ISO 8601 format\nconst today = new Date();\n\nconst start = new Date(\n  today.getFullYear(),\n  today.getMonth(),\n  today.getDate(),\n  0, 0, 0, 0\n).toISOString();\n\nconst end = new Date(\n  today.getFullYear(),\n  today.getMonth(),\n  today.getDate(),\n  23, 59, 59, 999\n).toISOString();\n\nreturn [{ json: { start, end } }];"
